sudo -u postgres psql postgres

postgres=# CREATE USER dev CREATEDB PASSWORD '1234;
postgres=# \q

If you're on Mac or Windows, dev

If you're on Linux/Vagarant, put your username in place of dev
  and change the username/password in ./Rakefile and ./config/database.rb accordingly

